casebody.data:
Dee Deidre FARMER, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT FOR the DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA. No. 18-8376. Supreme Court of the United States April 22, 2019. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied. Justice KAVANAUGH took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
